Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.17,0:00:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Go on, eat up.\NThey are known for their tasty weisswurst.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.84,0:00:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Like it? That's pretty good, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.72,0:00:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Your name is Dieter, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.93,0:00:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You eat up too, or Dieter will\Nfinish it off before you get any.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.35,0:00:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no need to worry, Dr. Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.31,0:00:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It's safe here.\NOnly regulars ever come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.03,0:00:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,If anyone new tries to come in,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.32,0:00:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Otto here will toss them out.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.24,0:00:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,If I always did that,\NI'd be out of business.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.62,0:00:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,-Who ordered the spätzle?\N-That was me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.67,0:00:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I set up a bed in the attic.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.75,0:00:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll sleep fine there\Nif you don't mind the mice.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.67,0:00:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Otto.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.43,0:00:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,He seems like a grump,\Nbut he's a nice guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.01,0:00:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you can't fight on an empty stomach.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.68,0:00:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for getting me a place to stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.35,0:01:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I should be thanking you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.44,0:01:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,If you hadn't saved me,\NI would be in the morgue now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.69,0:01:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Cheating death makes this meal\Neven more delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.70,0:01:11.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Go on, eat up.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.83,0:01:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I've contacted Dr. Gillen.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.20,0:01:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,He's also relieved that we found you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.21,0:01:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,He placed an ad in the papers\Nto try to contact you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.29,0:01:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,"Let us reminisce about when we cheated."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.17,0:01:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you seen it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.59,0:01:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.01,0:01:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Then why didn't contact him?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.43,0:01:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't want you\Nto get him caught up in this.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.52,0:01:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what friends are for,\Nespecially at times like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.40,0:01:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Earlier, you said\Nyou were keeping an eye on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.24,0:01:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That's because of\Nthe Richard Braun incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.74,0:01:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Richard's case?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.32,0:01:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. While he was on the police force,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.53,0:01:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,he shot and killed\Nthat young serial murder suspect.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.58,0:02:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,When I was reading the article about it,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.58,0:02:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Dieter saw the photo\Nof the young man who was shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.34,0:02:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,He said that boy was at Kinderheim 511.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.38,0:02:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What's Kinderheim 511?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.84,0:02:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,An orphanage in East Berlin.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.10,0:02:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,A very special one.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.81,0:02:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Dieter's foster father\Nwas one of the instructors there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.60,0:02:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,He had photos of all the children\Nwho had lived there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.85,0:02:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,This orphanage played a part\Nin these things?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.44,0:02:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Johan was there too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.23,0:02:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you mean there's a connection\Nbetween the boy Richard shot and Johan?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.91,0:02:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.62,0:02:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Before I was able to get any details\Nfrom Richard, he died.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.25,0:02:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It was at his grave that I spotted you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.75,0:02:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Poor Richard…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.75,0:02:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It's almost as if he brought us together.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.72,0:02:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,So far, you've had to fight alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.81,0:03:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,But you're not alone anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.98,0:03:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll prove your innocence.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.81,0:03:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Johan isn't far. I have a photo.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.27,0:03:11.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Darn it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.32,0:03:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I must've left it in the office.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.90,0:03:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,If you had seen the photo,\Nthat would've solved everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.70,0:03:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The man who came to kill you\Nprobably found it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.75,0:03:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Then it's gone now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.83,0:03:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,His name was Hess.\NI provided counseling to him and his wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.30,0:03:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I checked their number,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.80,0:03:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,but when I called,\Nthere was nobody there named Hess.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.05,0:03:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,So, Johan isn't far.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.47,0:03:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'll be able to see him. Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.89,0:03:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.35,0:03:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be able to see Johan face to face.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.03,0:05:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Thalbach & Schuwald AG.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.28,0:05:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the main company\Nin the Schuwald conglomerate.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.79,0:05:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Schuwald rarely ever shows his face,\Nbut he's been around a lot more lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.08,0:05:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,About this time every morning,\Nhe visits the subsidiary companies.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.92,0:05:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Richard found out before he died.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.97,0:05:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Not just this company,\Nbut all the conglomerate's companies
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.80,0:05:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,have grown immensely\Never since a certain young man
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.27,0:05:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,became Schuwald's, right-hand man.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.06,0:05:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Here they come.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.66,0:06:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,The man in the wheelchair is Schuwald.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.28,0:06:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,The one pushing him is Karl.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.12,0:06:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,And then there is…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.48,0:06:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,So, that's him?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.48,0:06:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,No doubt about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.86,0:06:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.99,0:06:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,-This is the first time.\N-Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.86,0:06:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the first time
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.41,0:06:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I've seen Johan in broad daylight.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.75,0:06:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that right? Then let's bring it all\Nout into the daylight!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.83,0:06:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Now's our only chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.34,0:07:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That's correct. Now's our only chance\Nto prove your innocence.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.26,0:07:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,However, you should remain in hiding\Nin the attic of Otto's restaurant for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.30,0:07:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll prove your innocence soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.77,0:07:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Richard's file is around here somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.06,0:07:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Here it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.86,0:07:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad I brought this home.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.57,0:07:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It won't be long now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.03,0:07:32.07,Default,,0,0,0,,We're almost there, Richard.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.16,0:07:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,We're on the verge of avenging your death.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.04,0:07:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,We have Johan in our sights.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.46,0:07:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,We also found Dr. Tenma, the key witness.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.96,0:07:44.21,Default,,0,0,0,,All that's left…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.92,0:07:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,All that's left is to find\Na witness to Richard's death that night.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.01,0:07:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,There must be someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.72,0:07:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Once we find them,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.14,0:07:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,we can prove that it was Johan\Nwho was with Richard when he died.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.06,0:07:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if we can't,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.60,0:08:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,there's that student Fahren, who claimed\Nhe was Schuwald's son and killed himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.57,0:08:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,If we could find the prostitute\Nthat Fahren visited, we could prove
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.16,0:08:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,that it was Johan that was with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.78,0:08:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's not all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.70,0:08:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,If we investigate the couple\Nwho claim to be Johan's parents,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.04,0:08:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,we can figure out\Nwho this Johan really is.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.29,0:08:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, we even found\NJohan Liebert's grave!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.71,0:08:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,We are closing the noose around\Nthis Johan's neck!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.64,0:08:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, Dr. Tenma,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.60,0:08:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,looking at you reminds me of Richard.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.06,0:08:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like you are carrying the weight\Nof the whole world on your shoulders.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.07,0:08:47.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember, you're not alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.49,0:08:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You have Dieter.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.07,0:08:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,And there is Dr. Gillen and me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.87,0:08:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything will be fine now.\NYou can sleep soundly tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.42,0:09:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't want\Nto get him caught up in this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.34,0:09:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.80,0:09:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the first time\NI have seen Johan in broad daylight.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.18,0:09:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Now's our only chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.06,0:09:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! Aren't you…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.44,0:09:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out now!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.82,0:09:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.42,0:09:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Reichwein speaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.75,0:09:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor, it's me, Gillen.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.75,0:09:50.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! I was just about to call you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.09,0:09:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm on my way over.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.80,0:09:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Tenma now?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.64,0:09:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,He's in the hideout I set up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.72,0:10:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Make certain he knows he should not leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.81,0:10:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Something's bothering me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.73,0:10:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,-Something is bothering me too.\N-Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.15,0:10:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems to me\Nthat Dr. Tenma isn't going after Johan
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.99,0:10:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,to prove his innocence.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.45,0:10:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to believe it,\Nbut I'm worried about the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.09,0:10:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Dieter.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.22,0:10:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.94,0:10:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Tenma told me to come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.07,0:10:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Tenma?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.36,0:10:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,-He left.\N-Where did he go?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.03,0:10:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,-He's going to kill him.\N-Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.95,0:10:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Tenma's going to kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.04,0:11:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop him!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.92,0:11:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Reichwein, stop him!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.42,0:11:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Tenma will end up a murderer!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.62,0:11:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.91,0:11:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be like that.\NI've got more for you, doc.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.12,0:11:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's where it gets really interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.62,0:11:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,No. You can tell me\Nin detail about it next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.75,0:11:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,My murder of the third woman\Nis the best of them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.76,0:11:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, doc!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.39,0:12:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.55,0:12:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to know what she sounded like\Nwhen I wrung her neck?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.52,0:12:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, doc!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.69,0:12:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,The story is great! You see, that woman…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.78,0:12:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Where have you gone, Tenma?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.66,0:12:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,At last, I've found you, Dr. Gillen.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.58,0:12:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.25,0:12:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I am Lunge. I am with the BKA.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.88,0:12:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I've heard about your work.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.76,0:12:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Several of the serial murderers\Nwho were my research subjects
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.59,0:12:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,were apprehended by you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.89,0:12:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,And I've read your book.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.19,0:12:49.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Why thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.77,0:12:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a remarkable work.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.11,0:12:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,The Psychology of Transcendental Crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.19,0:12:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,No other work examines
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.53,0:13:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,the mental state\Nof serial murderers as deeply as it does.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.66,0:13:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,In particular, chapter three,\Nthe case study of Heinz Kaul,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.12,0:13:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,on pages 262 to 294.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.87,0:13:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I was especially intrigued\Nby the connection of his childhood trauma
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.00,0:13:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,to the crimes he committed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.55,0:13:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,My, you know it quite well.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.34,0:13:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I am honored to know\Nyou read it so closely.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.35,0:13:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,The way I investigate involves\Nputting myself into the criminal's shoes
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.35,0:13:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,and thinking like they do\Nso I can predict their actions.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.52,0:13:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I can tell you are highly experienced.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.90,0:13:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd be glad to speak about it more\Nwhen I have more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.86,0:13:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Since neither of us have much time,\NI'll ask you this now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.62,0:13:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been visiting Munich a lot\Nlately, haven't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.58,0:13:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.92,0:13:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, have a seat. This won't take long.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.01,0:14:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You met with the psychologist\NDr. Reichwein the other day, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.59,0:14:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. He was one of\Nmy professors from the university.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.68,0:14:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,At Düsseldorf University?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.68,0:14:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.52,0:14:13.73,Default,,0,0,0,,When you attended Düsseldorf University,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.81,0:14:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,there was a very talented neurosurgeon\Nin your class, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.40,0:14:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you getting at?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.07,0:14:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you see Dr. Tenma?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.82,0:14:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.74,0:14:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,"Let us reminisce\Nabout when we cheated, Rudy."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.33,0:14:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You placed that classified ad\Nin all major newspapers across the country
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.63,0:14:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,from May 1 to 22.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.13,0:14:42.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I was quite surprised to find out
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.55,0:14:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,that brilliant people like you\Nand Dr. Tenma cheated as students.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.10,0:14:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It's amazing what close friends will do.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.77,0:14:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't say that Dr. Tenma\Nand I were close friends at university.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.69,0:15:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,In May of last year in Oder Park,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.61,0:15:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,with your help, the Velbert Police were\Nable to surround Dr. Tenma
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.03,0:15:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,and were on the verge of\Ncapturing him, but he got away.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.45,0:15:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,That's because\Nthe wire I wore malfunctioned.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.62,0:15:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That may have been how\Nyou helped him escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.33,0:15:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,He… Dr. Tenma is innocent.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.30,0:15:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.71,0:15:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Try to listen to me with an open mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.76,0:15:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The murders of
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.93,0:15:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,the Eisler Memorial Hospital director\Nand three others in Düsseldorf,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.51,0:15:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,the murder of a patient in\Na building under construction,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.52,0:15:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,the murder in Heidelberg,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.81,0:15:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,and the murders of middle-aged couples\Nacross Germany.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.27,0:15:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,None of those were committed by Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.94,0:15:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,As a criminal psychologist,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.40,0:15:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,this is the conclusion I came to\Nafter interviewing Tenma personally.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.95,0:15:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.37,0:15:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,So, where is he now?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.37,0:15:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,He has run off again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.25,0:15:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Why does he keep running?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.62,0:15:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Why does he run if he's innocent?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.54,0:16:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not running away!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.59,0:16:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Then why would he leave, even you,\Na close friend of his?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.39,0:16:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I have proof that he's not the murderer.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.43,0:16:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Have a look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.61,0:16:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my analysis\Nof all the details of this case.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.05,0:16:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Quite a considerable job.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.10,0:16:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,So, do you understand now?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.56,0:16:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.56,0:17:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,The odd death of Fahren,\Nwho claimed to be Schuwald's son.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.77,0:17:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The strange death of Richard Braun,\Nthe ex-detective investigating this case.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.45,0:17:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,The questions and rumors\Nabout Schuwald's illegitimate child.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.28,0:17:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a young man\Nat the center of all these things.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.95,0:17:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,When questioned by the police,\NTenma named him the real murderer.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.29,0:17:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Johan Liebert.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.96,0:17:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,But a grave for this very same\NJohan Liebert was found in Bruntal.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.30,0:17:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What's more, the person who took over\NRichard Braun's investigation,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.76,0:17:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Reichwein,\Nwas nearly killed the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.81,0:17:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand quite well.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.73,0:17:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,But you can't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.40,0:17:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll never prove\Nthat these separate incidents are related.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.03,0:17:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Tenma knows this quite well too,\Nwhich is why he has disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.08,0:18:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.01,0:18:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I notice how you drum your fingers.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.39,0:18:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let it bother you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.51,0:18:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I just use it to help me remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.77,0:18:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,As a psychologist,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.27,0:18:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I would say that your anxiety is\Nmanifesting in your finger drumming.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.86,0:18:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the same with me. But instead of\Ndrumming my fingers, I use this recorder.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.45,0:18:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,However,\Nwhat it records is completely objective.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.20,0:18:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,But in your case, what you remember\Nby drumming your fingers is
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.87,0:18:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,already tainted by your preconceptions.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.92,0:18:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet that's always\Nhow you've done your work.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.25,0:18:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You believe your memory is faultless\Nand that all your judgments are correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.59,0:18:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have a family?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.97,0:18:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What about hobbies?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.68,0:19:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Or do you only live for your work?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.39,0:19:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you ever made a mistake?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.48,0:19:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet you're terrified\Nof making a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.11,0:19:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,In your mind, Tenma must be a bad person.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.32,0:19:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,If he were not, then your\Nwhole world would fall to pieces.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.70,0:19:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Face the truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.91,0:19:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a photo of Johan Liebert.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.12,0:19:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you prove\Nthat Tenma made up everything?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.60,0:19:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,This young man…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.68,0:19:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,where is he now?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.14,0:19:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,He is a student at Munich University.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.27,0:19:48.07,Default,,0,0,0,,He is working as Schuwald's secretary now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.98,0:19:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I would like to keep this photo, if I may.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.49,0:19:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave the rest\Nof this matter to the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.91,0:20:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I may have made a terrible mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.04,0:20:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Dr. Tenma now?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.88,0:20:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,He should be in Munich.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.53,0:20:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Lunge here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.94,0:20:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Contact the Munich Police. I need\Nsome people on this case immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.49,0:20:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Tenma is somewhere in Munich now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.54,0:20:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,A sniper rifle?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.55,0:20:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no idea what you're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.09,0:21:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Heitmeyer at the mountain retreat\Nin Füssen called you about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.72,0:21:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Ten thousand marks upfront.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.06,0:21:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.27,0:21:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It won't be easy to get what you want,\Nso give me a week.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.49,0:21:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,,In the meantime,\Nget that pasty body of yours into shape.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.57,0:21:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if you got the best tools,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.54,0:21:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,they are worthless\Nif you cannot use them properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.13,0:21:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, for more news.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.59,0:21:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,The state's Chamber of Commerce\Nheld a posh reception
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.51,0:21:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,for political and business leaders\Nfrom around the world
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.59,0:21:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,who are here for the Munich\NElectronics Industry Trade Show.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.22,0:21:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,With the formation of the EU,\NBavarian industries are aiming
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.52,0:21:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,to become new media network leaders,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.60,0:21:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,which means this will be\Nthe largest trade fair yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.98,0:22:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,The reception was attended by\NHans Georg Schuwald,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.65,0:22:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,who has not appeared in public\Nfor the last 20 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.87,0:22:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,He was greeted with resounding applause.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.16,0:22:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Though Mr. Schuwald attended\Nin a wheelchair,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.12,0:22:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,he looked healthy\Nand showed these world leaders
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.13,0:22:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,he will be around for a while to come.
